@startuml --> UserRegistration : User is registered on the software platform. Use Case Flow: 1. The user navigates to the software platform's registration page. 2. The user enters their personal information such as name, email address, and password. 3. The user agrees to the terms and conditions of the software platform. 4. The user clicks on the "Register" button. 5. The software platform validates the user's information. 6. If the information is valid, the software platform creates a new user account and assigns a unique user ID. 7. The software platform sends a confirmation email to the user's email. 8. The user receives the confirmation email and clicks on the verification link to activate their account. 9. The software platform verifies the user's email address and activates their account. 10. The user is redirected to the login page.
@enduml